{"tid":2187725,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–無病無痛的話，人類是否會永生？","createTime":"2020-09-03T22:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:37:46.000Z","uid":38861,"like":83,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"fede780ef0a361378b018cefa4bd9987896239c2","tid":2187725,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T22:11:17.000Z","msg":"無病無痛，沒有任何交通或人為意外的話，人類是否會進入不死永生狀態呢？<br />\n<br />\n答案是，不會。<br />\n<br />\n箇中的原因，就是在於染色體亦即是DNA的運作機制之上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖1）正常人體細胞分裂的時候，染色體的長度會越來越短。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVatfp6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVatfp6.jpg&h=d75e0c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）染色體的頂端區域，我們稱之為Telomere。正常細胞分裂後，Telomere的長度便會越來越短，所以導致染色體的總長度亦會有所減少。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozNCTbP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozNCTbP.jpg&h=0ee8f273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）而幹細胞進行分裂的時候，則會有著Telomerase的協助，導致Telomere的長度便並不會有所減少。<br />\n然而，當幹細胞變成正常細胞後，Telomerase的功能便會消失。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgsWpiy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgsWpiy.jpg&h=288277e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）當Telomere長度削減到一定程度的時候，細胞便會自行啟動機制滅亡，又或者陷入衰老(Senescence)狀態。<br />\n<br />\n細胞滅亡或衰老的話，器官的功能便會衰退，最後亦會支撐不住，無法正常運作，促成死亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQHzaYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQHzaYB.jpg&h=b6225a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可能會問，現在科技如此倡明，那麼我們只要學習幹細胞的那一套方式，動用外力重啟Telomerase功能，那不就能踏入永生嗎？<br />\n<br />\n這個思路並沒有錯，只不過代價就是會增加患癌的風險。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，不少癌細胞的特徵就是Telomere長度非常之短，但又有著一定水平的Telomerase功能穩定維持著Telomere的長度，逃避進入滅亡的命運。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面的想，如果細胞真的是踏入「永生」狀態的話，終有一天無可避免會累積各種的DNA變異，促成癌細胞的誕生。<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）既然Telomere對細胞的壽命有著重要影響的話，那麼一些較為長壽的物種是否擁有較長的Telomere呢？<br />\n<br />\n科學家比較各物種的Telomere後（Ref1)，發現海豚的起始Telomere長度比人類高出6倍以上，但壽命長度始終是人類佔優。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fs3OLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fs3OLV.jpg&h=eb733cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而，決定物種壽命長度的其中一種因素，則是Telomere衰減的速度；<br />\nTelomere衰減的速度只是一個參考性的指標，並非絕對。物種的大小、新陳代謝機制的不同等等均會對壽命長度有著影響。<br />\n<br />\n人類每年約會減少71單位Telomere的長度，最高壽命為120歲。<br />\n而老鼠每年會減少7000單位Telomere長度，最高壽命為5歲。<br />\n<br />\n人類：每年減少71；120歲<br />\n大象：每年減少109；66歲<br />\n紅鸛：每年減少105；60歲<br />\n海豚：每年減少766；52歲<br />\n兀鷲：每年減少209；41歲<br />\n海鷗：每年減少771；25歲<br />\n馴鹿：每年減少531；22歲<br />\n山羊：每年減少363；21歲<br />\n老鼠：每年減少7000；5歲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n龜又是每年減少幾多呢？有待有心人發掘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjSWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=5bb3dad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjSWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=1fb79ba9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/116/30/15122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2F116%2F30%2F15122&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjSWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=973fd2ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/116/30/15122</a>"},{"pid":"e193a5de4cc175b308ff8a8e18b2e84c503861d4","tid":2187725,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T22:36:33.000Z","msg":"好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298bb81d448711d0df2c2f03d1a2b38071c7d021","tid":2187725,"uid":239345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"換哂人造器官🔪"},{"pid":"c0179dac130622e96dccc3501bce08742a142cc4","tid":2187725,"uid":75232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T22:41:22.000Z","msg":"呢個高質丫!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781ae3a3d77668215868f33a3fea084578111098","tid":2187725,"uid":8227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"298bb81d448711d0df2c2f03d1a2b38071c7d021","tid":2187725,"uid":239345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"換哂人造器官🔪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T23:17:16.000Z","msg":"當各種內臟器官<br />\n 連頭髮眼耳口鼻都換埋<br />\n咁仲算唔算係本身嗰個人？"},{"pid":"a9b0943eda0c6e028941a8dfa3f570a318b8bcb2","tid":2187725,"uid":160348,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T23:23:41.000Z","msg":"Subscribe 咗你，每朝睇一篇科普文，個人都勁啲，吹水多個話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ff58ccb2d70d57fbe4d9de87958af4e0dad6bd","tid":2187725,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T00:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a509dd9f0d9a3f0e2119acc14bf0a93d3457cfd","tid":2187725,"uid":264313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T